# frontend-developer Changelog

## 2025-12-27

### Changed
- Added `enforcing-react-19-conventions` to Tier 1 (Always Read)
  - Ensures React 19 code compliance on every task
  - Provides systematic reviewer checklist, required patterns, and anti-patterns detection
  - Line 31: Read call added to Tier 1 sequence
- Added `using-shadcn-ui` to Tier 3 Technology Triggers table
  - Trigger: "shadcn/ui components, Radix primitives"
  - Enables agent to install and customize shadcn/ui components (critical for Chariot platform)
  - Line 66: Trigger row added
- Added `using-context-api` to Tier 3 Technology Triggers table
  - Trigger: "Context API, global state, providers"
  - Provides React 19.2+ Context patterns and decision framework for Context vs Zustand/Query
  - Line 59: Trigger row added
- **Rationale**: Added 3 skills identified through semantic skill-finding analysis (enforcing-react-19-conventions 95% relevance, using-shadcn-ui 90%, using-context-api 85%)

## 2025-12-26

### Changed
- Added `securing-react-implementations` to Tier 3 Technology Triggers table
  - Trigger: "Security, XSS prevention, input sanitize"
  - Enables agent to load security patterns when working on frontend security concerns
- Added `integrating-tanstack-components` to Tier 3 Technology Triggers table
  - Trigger: "TanStack integration, component coordination"
  - Enables agent to load integration patterns when coordinating TanStack components
- Note: `enforcing-information-architecture` was already present in Tier 3 table (line 59)
